	Bureau of Labor Statistics\
The latest Producer Price Index news release has been posted on the BLS website at https://www.bls.gov/news.release/pdf/ppi.pdf and also archived at https://www.bls.gov/news.release/archives/ppi_01142026.pdf. Highlights are below.\
PPI for final demand advances 0.2% in November; goods rise 0.9%, services unchanged\
01/14/2026\
\
The Producer Price Index for final demand increased 0.2 percent in November. Prices for final demand goods advanced 0.9 percent, and the index for final demand services was unchanged. On an unadjusted basis, prices for final demand rose 3.0 percent for the 12 months ended in November.\
\
